{"kind":"article","seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Related Documentation","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ios.SeamComponents\/documentation\/SeamComponents\/SeamTheme","doc:\/\/ios.SeamComponents\/documentation\/SeamComponents\/SeamTheme\/Colors-swift.struct","doc:\/\/ios.SeamComponents\/documentation\/SeamComponents\/SeamTheme\/Fonts-swift.struct","doc:\/\/ios.SeamComponents\/documentation\/SeamComponents\/SeamTheme\/KeyCard-swift.struct","doc:\/\/ios.SeamComponents\/documentation\/SeamComponents\/GettingStarted"],"anchor":"Related-Documentation"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"SeamComponents"}],"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article","title":"Customizing Appearance"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Customize every aspect of SeamComponents’ appearance—including colors, fonts, and status indicators—using the composable SeamTheme system."}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SeamComponents provides a flexible theming system that allows you to fully customize the look and feel of all UI elements in the library. This enables easy white-labeling, brand alignment, and accessibility support."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Theming is accomplished by configuring a ","type":"text"},{"code":"SeamTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" value—which groups together all colors and fonts for the UI—and injecting it into your SwiftUI view hierarchy using the ","type":"text"},{"code":".environment(\\.seamTheme, ...)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" modifier.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Default behavior:"}]},{"type":"text","text":" If you don’t inject a theme, SeamComponents use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SeamTheme.default"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","type":"aside"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All SeamComponents (such as "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ios.SeamComponents\/documentation\/SeamComponents\/SeamAccessView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ios.SeamComponents\/documentation\/SeamComponents\/SeamKeyCardView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ios.SeamComponents\/documentation\/SeamComponents\/SeamCredentialsView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ios.SeamComponents\/documentation\/SeamComponents\/SeamUnlockCardView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":") automatically use the current theme for their appearance, so you can apply a consistent look across your app with just one line of code."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"text":"Why Theming Matters","level":2,"anchor":"Why-Theming-Matters","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Applying a custom theme allows you to:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"White-label your app","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" by replacing default colors and fonts with your brand’s identity."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Align your UI with your brand guidelines","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for a consistent and professional appearance."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Support accessibility features"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" such as Dynamic Type and high-contrast modes, ensuring your app is usable by everyone.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"text":"Quick Start","level":2,"anchor":"Quick-Start","type":"heading"},{"text":"Basic Custom Theme","level":3,"anchor":"Basic-Custom-Theme","type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Start from the default theme and override specific roles.","let myTheme = SeamTheme.default","    .with(colors: .default.with(accent: .orange))","    .with(fonts: .default.with(largeTitle: .system(size: 36, weight: .bold)))","","\/\/ Apply to your view hierarchy:","SeamAccessView()","    .environment(\\.seamTheme, myTheme)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Partial Customization","level":3,"anchor":"Partial-Customization","type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Override only what you need and keep the rest of the defaults:","let partialTheme = SeamTheme.default","    .with(colors: .default.with(accent: .green))","    .with(fonts: .default.with(body: .system(size: 16, weight: .medium)))","","SeamAccessView()","    .environment(\\.seamTheme, partialTheme)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"text":"Design Tips","level":2,"anchor":"Design-Tips","type":"heading"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Accent drives actions:"}]},{"text":" The ","type":"text"},{"code":"colors.accent","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" role powers primary buttons and highlights.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Prefer dynamic colors:"}]},{"type":"text","text":" Use light\/dark‑aware colors so your theme looks great in both appearances."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Keep fonts accessible:"}]},{"text":" Favor Dynamic Type–friendly fonts; avoid locking sizes unless necessary.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"level":2,"text":"Theme Scope and Environment","anchor":"Theme-Scope-and-Environment","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Themes in SeamComponents can be applied globally or scoped to a portion of your UI:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Global Theming:"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" Apply a theme at the root of your app’s view hierarchy to affect all SeamComponents.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Subtree Theming:"}]},{"text":" Apply a theme to a specific view or container to override the theme only for that subtree.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This flexibility allows you to easily customize appearance for entire apps or specific screens and components."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"level":2,"text":"FAQ","anchor":"FAQ","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Q: What happens if I don’t provide a theme?"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":"","type":"text"},{"text":"\n","type":"text"},{"text":"A: All SeamComponents will use the built-in default theme, which matches the native iOS style.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Q: Can I override only some colors or fonts?"}]},{"text":"","type":"text"},{"text":"\n","type":"text"},{"text":"A: Yes! SeamTheme is fully composable—provide only the values you want to override; everything else falls back to the default.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Q: Does theming work with accessibility features?","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":"","type":"text"},{"text":"\n","type":"text"},{"text":"A: Yes. All theme values work seamlessly with Dynamic Type, high-contrast settings, and other accessibility features.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Q: Can I change the theme at runtime?"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"text","text":"A: Absolutely. Because theming is driven by SwiftUI’s environment system, updating the theme dynamically will automatically update all affected SeamComponents."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"thematicBreak"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ios.SeamComponents\/documentation\/SeamComponents\/CustomizingAppearance"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ios.SeamComponents\/documentation\/SeamComponents"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/seamcomponents\/customizingappearance"]}],"references":{"doc://ios.SeamComponents/documentation/SeamComponents/SeamCredentialsView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ios.SeamComponents\/documentation\/SeamComponents\/SeamCredentialsView","abstract":[{"text":"Coordinates credential presentation and unlock flow.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","title":"SeamCredentialsView","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SeamCredentialsView","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SeamCredentialsView","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/seamcomponents\/seamcredentialsview","kind":"symbol"},"doc://ios.SeamComponents/documentation/SeamComponents/SeamTheme/Colors-swift.struct":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/ios.SeamComponents\/documentation\/SeamComponents\/SeamTheme\/Colors-swift.struct","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Colors"}],"title":"SeamTheme.Colors","url":"\/documentation\/seamcomponents\/seamtheme\/colors-swift.struct","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Colors"}],"abstract":[{"text":"A semantic palette for all SeamComponents, grouping all color values by purpose (e.g., accent, text, background, status, etc).","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://ios.SeamComponents/documentation/SeamComponents/SeamTheme/KeyCard-swift.struct":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"t